HEADWORD: Spoor
<hw>Spoor</hw> <pr>(sp⟦oomac⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>spoor</ets>; akin to AS. <ets>spor</ets>, G. <ets>spur</ets>, and
